---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import luckyImage from '@assets/lucky-surf-coach.jpg';
---

<article>
  <h3 class="heading">How I teach</h3>
  <div class="text">
    <p>
      I’m a certified ISA Level 1 instructor, with experience surfing both in
      Sri Lanka and abroad. My approach is simple: safe, friendly surf sessions
      that help you progress with confidence.
    </p>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Safety first</strong> — calm, supportive coaching so you feel comfortable
          and confident in the water
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Clear guidance</strong> — simple explanations in English, both on
          the beach and in the waves
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Theory to practice</strong> — we break things down on land, then
          apply it in the water
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Local knowledge</strong> — I grew up surfing Hiriketiya and know
          the bay inside out
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>Friendly progression</strong> — no pressure, just steady improvement
          while enjoying the ocean
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <Image
    src={luckyImage}
    alt="Lucky, certified surf instructor in Hiriketiya, holding a surfboard and smiling"
  />
</article>

<style>
  article {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;

    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    grid-template-areas:
      'title'
      'image'
      'text';

    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .heading {
    grid-area: title;
  }

  .text {
    grid-area: text;

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  img {
    grid-area: image;

    width: 100%;
    height: auto;

    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    article {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      grid-template-areas:
        'title image'
        'text image';

      padding: 0;
    }

    .heading {
      padding-top: 4rem;
      padding-left: 5rem;
    }
    .text {
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
      padding-left: 5rem;
    }

    img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;

      border-radius: 0rem;
    }
  }
</style>
